title Subsystem Class Diagram - SecuritySubsystem (ManageSystem)

class SecurityFacade <<facade>> {
  +checkPermission(operatorId: String, requiredPermission: String): boolean
}

class RBACAuthorizationService <<service>> {
  +verifyAccess(roleName: String, permission: String): boolean
}

class UserSessionManager <<service>> {
  +getActiveSession(userId: String): Object
}

SecurityFacade --> RBACAuthorizationService
SecurityFacade --> UserSessionManager
